&lt;li&gt;Document the results of component screening and testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtain and record test report data, reliability data, and supplier quality data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the development and implementation of processes to screen and test various component types for suitability in spaceflight applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit and receive Requests for Quote from external suppliers to conduct screening and testing of EEE components.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage component screening, from identification of requirements to documentation of results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtain and record test report data and reliability data of components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work among various internal departments to develop and conduct supplier audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document and record the results of supplier audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and document Supplier non-conformances, and work with deficient suppliers to achieve the requirements of Vast Space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and communicate the requirements of published industry standards as applicable to EEE parts used in the high-reliability environment of spaceflight applications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
