&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Establish and maintain electronic repository for supporting documentation related to all invoices and reimbursements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide excellent customer service to internal customers and Supplier inquiries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely responses to vendor emails and internal customer inquiries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the Finance team with other ad-hoc projects as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
