e on Earth furthering space exploration for humanity, come join us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vast is looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Avionics Design Reliability Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, reporting to the &lt;strong&gt;Sr. Manager of Design Reliability&lt;/strong&gt;, to guide the design, verification, and validation of Haven-1, the world&#39;s first commercial human-rated space station.&lt;/p&gt;
